OL,3,CThree people charged over arson attack
OL,4,Cin Wembley
OL,6,FThree people, including a 16-year-old
OL,7,Fboy, have been charged in connection
OL,8,Fwith an attempted arson attack on a
OL,9,FPersian media organisation in north-
OL,10,Fwest London.
OL,12,FOisin McGuinness, 21, Nathan Dunn, 19,
OL,13,Fand a 16-year-old boy, who are all
OL,14,FBritish nationals, have been charged
OL,15,Fwith arson with intent to endanger
OL,16,Flife, the Metropolitan Police said.
