OL,3,CThree people charged over arson attack
OL,4,Cin Wembley
OL,6,FIt comes after officers who were on
OL,7,Fpatrol at around 8.30pm on Wednesday
OL,8,Fwere told that an "ignited container"
OL,9,Fhad been thrown into the premises in
OL,10,FWembley and landed in the car park,
OL,11,Fthe force said.
OL,13,FThe suspects left the area in a black
OL,14,FSUV.
OL,16,FThe fire put itself out and no
OL,17,Finjuries were reported.
OL,19,FMcGuinness has also been charged with
OL,20,Fdangerous driving.
